  "body": "I just ran into the following issue while trying to fork Kovan using an Alchemy API\r\n\r\n```\r\n  Error: Invalid RpcBlockWithTransactions or null\r\n      at codec.decode.fold (/Users/dmihal/keystone/defi-777/contracts/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/hardhat-network/jsonrpc/types.ts:8:11)\r\n      at Left.fold (/Users/dmihal/keystone/defi-777/contracts/node_modules/io-ts/node_modules/fp-ts/lib/Either.js:113:16)\r\n      at Object.decode (/Users/dmihal/keystone/defi-777/contracts/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/hardhat-network/jsonrpc/types.ts:6:30)\r\n      at JsonRpcClient._perform (/Users/dmihal/keystone/defi-777/contracts/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/hardhat-network/jsonrpc/client.ts:230:27)\r\n      at process._tickCallback (internal/process/next_tick.js:68:7)\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe issue is also reported by @PatrickAlphaC here:\r\nhttps://ethereum.stackexchange.com/questions/89951/hardhat-deploy-script-works-on-testnet-but-not-on-forked-hardhat-network",
